{"tid":2462935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅高喊：「我就是中國人。」","createTime":"2021-03-26T10:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T11:48:51.000Z","uid":50275,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db2ea488f0611c4d59ae5848bcacd38e06a423ed","tid":2462935,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅(Eason)在香港宣傳新專輯，繼老婆徐濠縈惹火10萬大陸微博網友，他的新歌《非禮》也被解讀成在暗罵大陸人，他澄清沒有對大陸網友不禮貌，高喊：「我就是中國人。」沒有要攻擊任何人的意思，並自嘲是政治白癡。<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅昨(12日)在香港為《&hellip;3mm》舉行簽名會，因新歌《非禮》的歌詞中出現「到醫院插隊接生」、「蝗蟲螻蟻」字眼，被質疑根本在暗諷中國人，指民眾如蝗蟲過境；繼老婆徐濠縈在微博上大罵「沒禮貌的中國人」後，兩人的一舉一動引起爭議，還被媒體形容為「敢死隊夫妻」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，陳奕迅解釋《非禮》歌詞只是希望大家都能以禮相待，「蝗蟲螻蟻」則是說霸氣的蝗蟲與蟻民，不一樣的人也要尋找默契好好相處，強調根本並沒有攻擊任何人的意思，他也說：「我就是中國人，中國人不打中國人。」"},{"pid":"904cbbd63d70395d77bce49072bae3d96f821571","tid":2462935,"uid":301632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 諗起比比鳥 家下輸晒兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7ab252a043725a06786ae260324c07e3032247","tid":2462935,"uid":286131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國人不打中國人?<br />\n中國人<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">最愛</span></span></strong>打中國人<br />\n中國人<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">只敢</span></span></strong>打中國人"},{"pid":"82815d45da2f8aa23062e55411b000036edd28fd","tid":2462935,"uid":64072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"中國人不打中國人，咁中國編出嚟嘅歷史係打邊個？近排話要武統台灣又係打邊個？"},{"pid":"0c9e5c917aca2040cd83cb13fec694928d05d1c3","tid":2462935,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"海報「統一」台灣<br />\n<br />\n2014年4月中旬，陳奕迅在其facebook專頁，上載其「Eason's LIFE in China」宣傳海報，列出此年在中國的巡迴演唱會時間與城市。在其照片後結合中國地圖，不料地圖卻見到台灣也列在其中，成為中國版圖的一部份。"},{"pid":"6d9c216e608bac3b67856162728ade37dfc0f3ef","tid":2462935,"uid":54975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:15:29.000Z","msg":"但唔係中國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea39d50bd59dcfd94c161216a2cbe57140379acf","tid":2462935,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"2014年7月下旬，陳奕迅在台灣一個節目上，自爆兩年後暫別歌壇：「我還有兩張專輯，在合約期裡面，我做完真的要休息了，不想再做專輯，應該說我不想再工作了。」還即場請觀眾做見證人。"},{"pid":"e3c589f5f4679716840a0450600bcfd7331021b6","tid":2462935,"uid":395191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"一件垃圾吹到上天"},{"pid":"4076d9221bb0cd006948f2acac9325f5fb7102f3","tid":2462935,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:22:51.000Z","msg":"第二個家係英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f708a55da15784040a7fdc5605d2dab7187250e6","tid":2462935,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"中囯係世界各國一部分"},{"pid":"18c2fbd7bc2829be7b45ede5ab1f8382c37069b8","tid":2462935,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅是共匪，他全家都是共匪，共匪全黨死清光"},{"pid":"a3ac5604be63087156d7cd3a3d1d15b8702f87c7","tid":2462935,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:35:34.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔鍾意聽佢啲歌,覺得佢份人太串,依家仲要奶共.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aebdec0a3638f934dc2811eb2bef7c3f1a469f1","tid":2462935,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZddrYEwCzULL4DyxKYNsXoXTykY9S1waNGnUpsNxFF3X?filename=mEPV8mQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEPV8mQ.jpg&h=2dcf731e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59c5471fa137ab6e061a14d7e2c04dd21b7a741c","tid":2462935,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11: